<Product Name>Creative Zen 16 GB (Black)
<Title>I'm in heaven
<Date>Sun Feb 17 00:00:00 CST 2008
<Content>I have had other creative players but this one by far blows them away and the best aspect is that it starts playing the minute I power it up. I will reccomend the screen protector, especillay for a screen this size. This player is easy to navigate and easy to load music, I basically do drag and drop and I'm ready to go. My last player was a Sansa E280 and it froze up a lot and I couldn't organize music the way I wanted to to, that is no longer the problem with this unit. The price is very reasonable for 16gb of Flash Memory, you can't go wrong with this player.  
<Overall>5

