<Product Name>Creative Zen 16 GB (Black)
<Title>Creative Zen 16g Much better than Ipod Nano
<Date>Fri Feb 22 00:00:00 CST 2008
<Content>This items is one of the best players in its type I ever saw and use.   1. It reproduces divx video  1.1 I f you have subtitule files, it also reproduce they as well. 2. You don't need Itunes to load music to the player 3. FM Radio! 4. Much better video resolution than its similar Ipod Nano 5. 16gb for the same price as the 8gb Ipod nano 6. Do I have to say more?  The software that came with the player its really easy to use, and it actually adds usefull tools to the windows explorer.  It may be not as little as the Nano, but it really worth the price  
