<Product Name>Creative Zen 16 GB (Black)
<Title>Great product
<Date>Tue Jan 01 00:00:00 CST 2008
<Content>Bought this for my son for Christmas. He's had a Zen Micro for years and thought he wanted to switch to a Zune. I didn't know this until after I had already purchased the Zen, so told him he could exchange the Zen if he didn't want it. He loves this Zen, so kept it. Says the battery life has been excellent and loves the size...not too small, not too big. Beautiful display. Only negative is the earphones...you'll want to purchase different ones.  
