<Content>I love this player! I did not want an ipod. I wanted to just play mp3 that i owned with no drm on them or restrictions. I LOVE how it syncs up with Windows Media Player. This is so cool -- I can rip all my songs from my CD's directly into Media Player easily and it makes it easy to get the album art and track listings. And pictures in my media library are there as well --- then i just plug in the usb of the zen and it syncs them right up. PLAYLISTS and ALBUM ART -- are in there and come across. I was worried this was a feature that only ipod had. This ZEN is awesome and such a low price! Yes the usb cable is very short and I did not like the ear phones --- but this player rocks! plus i was worried that the volume would not go up enough to listen to some music loud and use speakers --- BUT you can easily shut the volume limiting off. So the fears i had about buying one --- have ALL been resolved. This thing has a large screen and is great. It is a good idea to get a screen protecter. and do not buy this from anyone else --- AMAZON is the greatest --- if you have any problems at all --- THEY WILL HELP YOU LIKE NO OTHER!!!! You will be amazed at how such a big company really acts like they care about your piddly small order. THEY ROCK!!!!!!!!  
